My Real Estate Agency secured the assistance of Techpertz IT Solutions in 2019, applying key word searches and other misc. SSO and SMO work.  After their work, we did experience more traffic.

Later in 2023, my website went down.  GoDaddy who holds my Domains, was somewhat helpful, but could not pinpoint the primary cause.The numerous calls to them were absorbing my busy days causing overwhelming frustrations.

I contacted Joe at Techpertz.  He immediately jumped on board!  Tackling the combination of causes for our downed website.  I am not techy, but understood the problem had to do with an SSL certificate, and Hosting issue from one domain, that was no longer defaulting (forwarding) to our primary website, as we originally set up years ago.  I am sure there were other misc. connections that also had to be reestablished.  For 2.5 days Joe was very dilegent in working out these problems, not giving up until our website was live once again.

Joe even added our new logo to the website that I could not figure out how to upload due to new platform changes.

Thank you Joe for your persistent dedication, even 3 years after our initial contracted work.  It's great having a real person I can call, who has a direct phone no. and personal email to quickly work out a serious downed website problem... rather than an automated helpline; waiting, pushing buttons, being transferred around to different specialty reps., re-explaining the problems again and again each call i had to make.  Then trying to explain what I see V.S. the ability to personally send a screen shot or photo like I was able to do with Techpertz IT Solutions.

You would assume this service would have come with a big price tag.  It didn't!

Thanks again Joe!
